        dc:description           "Figures 1–5. Gangliostoma spp. 1–3. G. abaxialispura Xu, Huang & Guo, sp. nov. 1. Oral view. 2. Lateral view. 3. Part enlargement of marginal tentacles. 4. Part enlargement of the subumbrella of G. dayaensis Xu, Huang & Du, 2010 (after Du et al., 2010). 5. Part enlargement of the subumbrella of G. guangdongensis Xu, 1983 (after Xu, 1983). Abbreviation: p—papilla; g—gonad; t—tentacle. Scale bars=2.0mm." ;
